patient samples, an approach dictated by the highly variable genome of the target pathogen. Genomic data and phylogenetic reconstructions were communicated immediately to Nigerian authorities and the World Health Organization to inform the public health response. Real-time analysis of 36 genomes and subsequent confirmation using all 120 samples sequenced in the country of origin revealed extensive diversity and phylogenetic intermingling with strains from previous years, suggesting independent zoonotic transmission events and thus allaying concerns of an emergent strain or extensive human-to-human transmission.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Kafetzopoulou, L. E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Pullan, S. T.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lemey, P.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Suchard, M. A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ehichioya, D. U.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Pahlmann, M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Thielebein, A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hinzmann, J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Oestereich, L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wozniak, D. M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Efthymiadis, K.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Schachten, D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Koenig, F.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Matjeschk, J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lorenzen, S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lumley, S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ighodalo, Y.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Adomeh, D. I.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Olokor, T.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Omomoh, E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Omiunu, R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Agbukor, J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ebo, B.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Aiyepada, J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ebhodaghe, P.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Osiemi, B.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ehikhametalor, S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Akhilomen, P.", "affiliation": null}, {"name"